                TextColor="#ACB1BB"/>

            <Label Margin="0,20,0,0"
                FontSize="13"                
                TextColor="#ACB1BB">
                I like exploring different mediums, from acrylic painting to digital illustration and getting lost in the pages of fantasy novels and thought-provoking poetry.
